  • Classes in starkcoder.failfast.fails used by starkcoder.failfast.fails 
    Class and Description
    AFailer
    Abstract implementation of IFailer.
    AFailFastException
    Abstract implementation of fail-fast exception inheriting RuntimeException.
    IFail
    Type specification for a fail that matches a single check.
    IFailer
    Failer specification.
    IFailerCustomizer
    This specifies runtime customizations to {link:NFail} attributes of the various failer specifications.
    IFailerObserver
    This is a specification for instances that would like to be notified when an exception is about to be thrown.
    IFailerPublisher
    This is a specification for managing IFailerObserver's that needs to notified when an exception is about to be thrown.
    IFailFastException
    Specification of a fail-fast exception.
    IFailFastExceptionReference
    Specifies a reference to the first thrown fail-fast exception.
    NFail
    Annotates fail-methods in failers.
